Ranger Help for: heartshot
==========================

SYNTAX:      heartshot <target>
USAGE:       Any terrain
SLOT COST:   NA
BASE SP:     variable
SKILL TYPE:  archery

SUMMARY:
This skill allows a Ranger to fire a precisely aimed crossbow bolt at
the target's heart. The Ranger must be wielding a crossbow and carrying
at least one bolt.

Heartshot is a deliberate finishing shot, not a rapid-fire attack. It
uses the best bolt available and deals heavy single-target damage based
on dexterity, Ranger progression, crossbow quality, and bolt quality. A
poorly lined up shot still clips the target for partial damage, while a
clean shot is much stronger. Heartshot is especially dangerous against
targets that are already wounded.
